@startuml
title Agri Watch - System Context

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F7F9FC
  BorderColor #3F4E5E
}
skinparam actor {
  BorderColor #3F4E5E
  BackgroundColor #EAF2F8
}

left to right direction

actor Farmer
actor "Agricultural adviser" as Adviser
actor "System administrator" as Admin

rectangle "Agri Watch\nAgriculture AI Helper" as System

rectangle "European Commission\nRSS and Atom feeds" as EU
rectangle "UK government\nfeeds" as UK
rectangle "USDA and other\nofficial feeds" as USDA

Farmer --> System : Ask agriculture questions
Adviser --> System : Search policy, funding,\ndeadlines and changes
Admin --> System : Start ingestion\nand rebuild index

System --> Farmer : Answer, matching articles\nand source links
System --> Adviser : Grounded summary,\ncategories and dates

System --> EU : Fetch published updates
System --> UK : Fetch published updates
System --> USDA : Fetch published updates

note bottom of System
The tool helps users discover and summarize
agriculture information. It does not replace
official legal or professional advice.
end note

@enduml
